pretty important when it comes to dungeon exploration.

【Experienced Adventurer B】 Weapons have their own characteristics.
It's best to take something that's easy for you to use.

【Experienced Adventurer B】 First, let's talk about swords...
The characteristic of a sword is that you can \C[18]parry\C[0] and \C[18]counterattack\C[0].

【Experienced Adventurer B】 When there are multiple opponents,
this becomes quiet effective.

【Experienced Adventurer B】 Next, let's talk about maces...
The characteristic of a mace's that it occasionally \C[18]stuns\C[0] the opponent.

【Experienced Adventurer B】 If you manage to stun your opponent,
you can beat even the strongest enemies with ease.
However, be careful as there are unstunnable monsters.
Slimes are a prime example of that.

【Experienced Adventurer B】 Lastly, let's talk about daggers...
The characteristic of a dagger is inflicting \C[18]bleeding\C[0]
damage to the opponent.

【Experienced Adventurer B】 The attack power of a dagger itself is low,
but you can find daggers that have poison or burning effects.
So, if you find one, try it.

【Experienced Adventurer B】 It has more power than it looks.
However, be careful as you won't be able to equip
a shield for defense.

【Experienced Adventurer B】 That's about it.
Understanding the characteristics of weapons and choosing
the right one is the key to conquering dungeons.
Good luck!
